ets updated</li>\n<li>UpdateKit is not integrated</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Direct Download RH Pros</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Has a better user interface</li>\n<li>Options to download many more popular Shortcuts </li>\n<li>Updates Frequent</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Direct Download RH:</th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Pros</strong></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td><strong>Cons</strong></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1. Better UI</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td>1. A little slower</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2. More Download Options</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td>2.</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3. Updates Frequent</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td>3.</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>DependKit:</th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Pros</strong></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td><strong>Cons</strong></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1. Has an explanatory <a href=\"https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/3258c755d1b44ec5b00b6520836ea042\">Demo Shortcut</a></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td>1. Currently broken</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2. More downloads</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td>2. Rarely gets updated</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3. A little faster (when works)</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td>3. UpdateKit isn't integrated</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Integrating Direct Download RH</h2>\n<p>3 Simple Steps</p>\n<p><em>Link: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/2OAsYJB2qZY\">Video Demonstration with Demo Shortcut</a></em></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Press “Get Download Link” </li>\n<li>\n<p>The link will then be copied to your clipboard. (You can ignore the download option.)\n<img alt=\"Present Download\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9nW2zz4.jpg\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go into another Shortcut and follow this picture:</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img alt=\"Testing Example\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CYL2ER7.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Banners</h2>\n<p><strong>Required; White</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2002\"><img alt=\"R, W\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nchQBAm.png\"></a></p>\n<p>Markdown Code<br>\n<code>[![R, W](https://i.imgur.com/nchQBAm.png)](https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2002)</code></p>\n<p><strong>Required; Black</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2002\"><img alt=\"R; B\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8fl6twd.png\"></a></p>\n<p>Markdown Code\n<code>[![R; B](https://i.imgur.com/8fl6twd.png)](https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2002)</code></p>\n<hr>\n<p><img alt=\"Direct Shortcut\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j7Bfs8R.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/1841\"><img alt=\"W Feedback Banner\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/00ahDjl.png\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/1911\"><img alt=\"Credits to MediaKit\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D43UmNN.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://routinehub.co/user/AShortcuts\"><img alt=\"Author AShortcut\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hX2x10B.jpg\"></a></p>\n\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>2.6 - June 12, 2019, 12:41 a.m.</strong></p><p><br>Version 2.6 Release Notes<br>- Removed Direct Download  SS option for now<br>- Optimized some of the settings<br>- Sorry guys but vcf menus probably aren’t coming since they increase the file size of the Shortcut by a lot</p>"}